  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "JUNIOR INTERIOR DESIGNER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Singaporean / PR / Malaysian</strong><br /><strong>Fresh graduates or those with no experience are welcome!</strong><br /></p><p>Looking to kickstart your career in interior design? Join <strong>The Interior Place</strong>, one of Singapore’s most experienced and trusted interior design firms with <strong>26 years of expertise</strong> and thousands of completed homes.</p><p>We provide <strong>comprehensive onboarding, 1-to-1 mentorship, and guaranteed renovation leads</strong> to help you grow confidently in your design career.<br /></p><p><strong>What You’ll Enjoy</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Stable Basic Salary + Attractive Commission Scheme</strong></li><li><strong>Guaranteed at least 80 renovation leads per year</strong></li><li><strong>1-to-1 Mentorship and Training</strong> from experienced designers</li><li><strong>Ongoing Product & Materials Training</strong></li><li><strong>Flexible Working Hours</strong></li><li><strong>Attractive Staff Benefits</strong> and <strong>Career Growth Opportunities</strong></li><li><strong>Supportive, Collaborative & Creative Work Culture</strong></li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in meeting clients and understanding their design needs</li><li>Support in preparing design concepts, mood boards, and 3D drawings</li><li>Work closely with senior designers on project execution</li><li>Help coordinate with suppliers, contractors, and site teams</li><li>Learn to manage timelines, budgets, and quality standards</li></ul><p><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Interior Design (preferred- but not compulsory)</li><li>Creative, detail-oriented, and eager to learn</li><li>Good communication and presentation skills</li><li>Passionate about interior design and home styling</li><li>No prior experience needed — <strong>training will be provided!</strong></li></ul><p>Ready to design your future?<br />✨ <strong>Apply now and start your interior design journey with us!</strong></p>",
